# Cargo build artifacts for this standalone crate.
/target

# Cargo build artifacts for the standalone icongen/ icon-generator crate.
/icongen/target

# Packaging outputs from bundle.sh. The .app bundle, the .dmg, the generated
# AppIcon.iconset/ and AppIcon.icns are all BUILD OUTPUTS — never committed.
# Only the packaging SCRIPT (bundle.sh), the Info.plist template, the icon
# SOURCE (assets/icon.svg), the icongen/ crate source, and this .gitignore are
# tracked. Re-create the artifacts any time with `bash bundle.sh`.
/dist
